[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Number industries]]
Sets the frequency of industries for a new map.<br><br>
0 = none<br>
1 = very low<br>
2 = low<br>
3 = normal {default}<br>
4 = high<br>
<pre>
[difficulty]
number_industries = 3
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [ 0 | 1 | 2 | 3 | 4 ]

'''Default:''' 3


